import React, { useState } from "react";
import {
  Collapse,
  Navbar,
  NavbarToggler,
  NavbarBrand,
  Nav,
  UncontrolledDropdown,
  DropdownToggle,
  DropdownMenu,
  DropdownItem,
  NavbarText,
} from "reactstrap";

const Navi = (props) => {
  const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false);

  const toggle = () => setIsOpen(!isOpen);

  return (
 
      <Navbar color="light" light expand="md">
        <NavbarBrand href="/">Ana Sayfa</NavbarBrand>
        <NavbarToggler onClick={toggle} />
        <Collapse isOpen={isOpen} navbar>
          <Nav className="mr-auto" navbar>
            <UncontrolledDropdown nav inNavbar>
              <DropdownToggle nav caret>
                Tanımlar
              </DropdownToggle>
              <DropdownMenu right>
                <DropdownItem>Tesis Alanı-Lokasyonlar</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Mahal Tipi Tanımı</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Tesis Tipi Tanımı</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Hizmet Tanımı</DropdownItem>
              </DropdownMenu>
            </UncontrolledDropdown>
            <UncontrolledDropdown nav inNavbar>
              <DropdownToggle nav caret>
                Denetim İşleri
              </DropdownToggle>
              <DropdownMenu right>
                <DropdownItem>Option 1</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Option 2</DropdownItem>
              </DropdownMenu>
            </UncontrolledDropdown>
            <UncontrolledDropdown nav inNavbar>
              <DropdownToggle nav caret>
                Uygunsuzluk & DÖF
              </DropdownToggle>
              <DropdownMenu right>
                <DropdownItem>Option 1</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Option 2</DropdownItem>
              </DropdownMenu>
            </UncontrolledDropdown>
            <UncontrolledDropdown nav inNavbar>
              <DropdownToggle nav caret>
                Yönetici İşlemleri
              </DropdownToggle>
              <DropdownMenu right>
                <DropdownItem>Option 1</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Option 2</DropdownItem>
              </DropdownMenu>
            </UncontrolledDropdown>
            <UncontrolledDropdown nav inNavbar>
              <DropdownToggle nav caret>
                Administrator
              </DropdownToggle>
              <DropdownMenu right>
                <DropdownItem>Option 1</DropdownItem>
              </DropdownMenu>
            </UncontrolledDropdown>
          </Nav>
          <NavbarText>test@gmail.com</NavbarText>
        </Collapse>
      </Navbar>
    
  );
};  

export default Navi;
